column3: NSLOCTEXT("", "76A23AA948BE18D1663901B2C98834E4", "Why did you let him lock us up here Starlight?")
NSLOCTEXT("", "76BACEBC417B0AC2CF862DBE0FE443F8", "We shouldn\'t have let him boss us around. This is MY castle. He can\'t do this kind of stuff.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "5504613548213CD80D7BC3A764E9493A", "I think he needs our help. After all, he\'s here in this world with the rest of us. Something must be wrong.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "1F51390F4A45095FA39FF0A5C2958993", "We could have helped him without letting him lock us up.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "B2D3DB2E453E2B9F3E6F3CA6EC854B39", "This place doesn\'t seem so stable...")
NSLOCTEXT("", "0C06373D40D9650600C2CF9B50FABDF2", "Guess this can\'t be my castle then. No way my home would be this crumbly.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "4E89896E4C63C45E5C5A218361BE4B98", "Well, we have to get out of here. Helios needs to know the castle\'s falling apart.")
NSLOCTEXT("", "F852A0AB47B79BA23FEFE0BA2CE159BF", "What are you talking about? Who cares what happens to that jerk?")
NSLOCTEXT("", "ED0C42D04A11504DFCA3CB82C39C00C5", "I care, and you should too!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "D606A79B4ADF25F7C4138383F51955DD", "All I care about is getting out of here!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "AD91EEA143E780F5DC10F3AB48C57ED6", "We all want to get out of here but we have to take him with us!")
NSLOCTEXT("", "8B9D3EDC43F7B09EC345F688A4B60B86", "He\'ll find his own way out!")
